    images: ["https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0348/4948/9034/files/TB_Victrix_XB_GambitPrime_TB_A__Standard_Header_3000x3000_b83656f8-95ea-4821-b14c-e9a241f15bb5.jpg?v=1779671578", "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0348/4948/9034/files/TB_Victrix_XB_GambitPrime_TB_A_Standard_01_3000x3000_WorldsFastest.jpg?v=1779671576", "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0348/4948/9034/files/TB_Victrix_XB_GambitPrime_TB_A_Standard_02_3000x3000_Fit-Your-PlayStyle_e3b06152-c196-469f-8541-afb638cf079a.jpg?v=1779671597"],
    bodyHtml: `<p>When the speed of your input could be the difference between a win and a loss, you need the world’s fastest licensed Xbox controller. The Gambit Prime Wired Tournament Controller by Victrix is the best option for competitive and esports gamers who demand speed, precision, customization, and performance.<br></p>
<p>Officially licensed by Xbox and compatible with Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, &amp; Windows 10/11 PCs, the Victrix Gambit Prime is built for gamers who want to dominate the competition!<br></p>
<p>Lightning-Fast Dual Core™ Technology<br>The Gambit Prime delivers unmatched speed with Dual Core™ Technology. One core powers ultra-fast input processing while the other ensures crystal-clear audio. As the world’s fastest officially licensed Xbox controller, it gives you the competitive edge to dominate every match. </p>
<p>Fully Customizable Design<br>Take control of your game with 12 interchangeable components, allowing you to fine-tune your setup for peak performance. Customize your playstyle with 2 back paddles (2-button or 4-button), 2 standard sticks (1 dome and 1 sniper), 2 circular gates, 2 octagonal gates, 1 diamond D-pad, and 1 cross D-pad, giving you precision where it matters most. With a dedicated spare parts case, you’ll always be tournament ready!</p>
<p>Dolby Atmos Audio<br>The Gambit Prime takes game audio to the next level with a built-in Dolby Atmos and a lifetime subscription. Experience 3D spatial sound through the 3.5mm headset jack that puts you in the center of action, letting you hear every footstep, reload, and enemy movement before they even see you. </p>
<p>Precision-Tuned Clutch Hair Triggers<br>React faster and take control with Clutch Triggers™, featuring five adjustable trigger stops including a hair-trigger mode for lightning-fast response. Fine-tune sensitivity to match your playstyle, whether you need rapid fire for FPS or full-range motion for racing. With precision at your fingertips, you’ll always have a competitive edge!</p>
<p>Victrix Control Hub App<br>Take customization to the next level with the free Victrix Control Hub App on Xbox and PC. Remap buttons, adjust trigger sensitivity, find-tune dead zones, and optimize audio settings all in one app. Run diagnostics and update firmware to keep your controller performing at its peak.</p>
<p>Package Contents:<br>•    Turtle Beach® Victrix™ Gambit Prime Controller<br>•    Detachable 3m Braided USB-C Cable<br>•    12 Interchangeable Components: D-Pad, Thumbsticks, Back Paddles, and Gates <br>•    Spare Parts Case<br>•    Quick Start Insert</p>
<p>Technical Specifications:<br>•    Average Digital Input Latency: 2.1ms<br>•    Average Analog Input Latency: 2.4ms<br>•    Connection: 3m Wired USB-C Connection<br>•    Audio Input/Output: 3.5mm 4-pole Headset Jack, Dolby Atmos (Lifetime Subscription included)<br>•    Processor: 500 MHz Dual Core ARM-7 Victrix proprietary MCU, firmware upgradeable<br>•    RF Wireless Transceiver: 2.4 GHz Dual Core Victrix proprietary SOIC<br>•    Product Weight (controller): 265g / 0.58lb <br>•    Product Dimensions (controller) (W x H x D):  <br>o    6.3” x 4.1” x 2.4” <br>o    160mm x 105mm x 60mm <br></p>`,
