    bodyHtml: `<p>PREMIUM SOUND FOR THE PEOPLE<br>Experience the perfect fusion of best-in-class sound and fearless design. Our latest earbud doesn’t just keep up — it leads. Introducing Method 360 ANC with Sound by Bose: engineered for incredible audio and nonstop action.<br><br>SOUND BY BOSE<br>We teamed up with Bose to bring you a high-fidelity audio experience defined by clarity of sound and depth of range. Everything from ear gels to audio architecture is optimized for ideal performance. No compromises, just great sound.<br><br>SUPERIOR ACTIVE NOISE CANCELING<br>Welcome to next-level noise cancelation. Eliminate the world around you and sink into an undisturbed listening experience. Need to tune into your surroundings? Turn on Adjustable Stay-Aware Mode instead.<br><br>CLIP-ANYWHERE DESIGN<br>Clip It and Rip It with effortless carry and stand-out style. Our signature slider case and O-ring design clips to your backpack, key ring or pants so it's always close-at-hand and ready for action with a look that shouts Skullcandy.<br><br>TAP, TUNE, TRANSFORM<br>Unlock Method 360 ANC’s full potential with the Skull-iQ App. Choose one of 3 preset EQ’s or customize your own, reconfigure the button functions, adjust your Stay-Aware Mode and more.<br><br>CUSTOMIZE YOUR FIT<br>Included ear gels and fit fins in three sizes let you dial in the perfect fit, so you stay locked in and comfortable no matter how hard you go.<br></p>`,
