    bodyHtml: `<p>CRUSH THE ACTION WITH MIND-BENDING BASS<br>Meet Crusher 540 Active, the ultimate active-use headphones designed to help you get in the zone to enhance your workout. Feel every beat with Crusher's adjustable sensory bass, pushing you to go harder when the workout gets tough. With a sweat and water-resistant nano-coating, Crusher 540 Active stays durable through your most intense sessions. Plus, its breathable fabric earpads keep you cool and comfortable when things heat up. Crush every beat, crush every workout.<br><br>MIND-BENDING BASS, TUNED FOR MOVEMENT<br>Tune out the burn and crush every workout. Adjustable Crusher Bass delivers total audio immersion to power through the pain with the original, one-and-only multi-sensory bass experience in these headphones.<br><br>READY FOR SWEAT. BUILT TO LAST<br>Crusher 540 Active headphones don’t flinch at rep or rain. A sweat- and water-resistant nano-coating shields your gear at the gym or outside, while breathable ear cushions and an easy-clean headband keep things fresh—workout after workout.<br><br>GRIP THAT DOESN'T QUIT<br>Power through your toughest training with up to 40 hours of battery life. Rapid Charge delivers 4 hours of playtime with a quick 10-minute charge, so your musical motivation never ends before your workout.<br><br>CRUSH IT YOUR WAY<br>Use the Skullcandy App to unlock Crusher 540 Active’s full potential. Personalize your Sound to your unique hearing and select your preferred EQ mode.<br><br>FLAT-FOLDING, READY TO ROLL<br>Crusher 540 Active Headphones fold down small to go wherever your crew takes you. Toss it in your gym bag, or favorite skate pack—this is peak portability with zero compromise.<br><br></p>`,
