    bodyHtml: `<p>AI Touch Interaction Experience<br>Touch to Control, Shoot with Ease<br><br>Live Feed Monitoring<br>Remote touchscreen access lets you control it freely from 10m / 33ft away.<br><br>Versatile Control at Your Fingertips<br>The 1.22" full-color touchscreen offers high-definition AI live feeds, intuitive control of the gimbal and phone camera, all in one streamlined interface. It also supports an access to tutorial.<br><br>Let Fill Light Set the Mood<br>Remote Light Control. High-brightness in cool, warm, and neutral tones. Seamless dimming for perfect light, down to every detail<br><br>360° Infinite Pan Tracking<br>With 360° infinite pan tracking, your movements are always in frame — perfect for capturing sweeping landscapes or automatic recording in daily life and work.<br><br>Full-Angle Shooting<br>205mm Built-in Extension Pole. Easily fit the whole group in the frame or switch between high and low angles for dynamic clips.<br><br>iSteady 9.0 Anti-Shake Stabilization System<br>Upgraded for Smoother Shots<br><br>Specifications<br>Weight: 428g (±5g)<br>Material: High-performance composite material (Extension pole: 6063-H aluminum alloy)<br>Payload: 400g<br>Smartphone Width: 58mm~98mm<br>Battery Capacity: 7.4V/1600mAh<br>Charging Time: 2.5h<br>Runtime: Approx. 9 hours (Balanced and stationary); 4~5 hours (With AI tracking and fill light used simultaneously)<br>Controllable Range Pan: 360° infinite Tilt：120° Roll：330°<br>Working Temperature -10~45℃<br>Motor Protection: The gimbal will automatically shut down in case of improper operation to protect the motor.<br>Standard Accessories<br>iSteady V3 Ultra*1, AI tracker*1, Touchscreen remote controller*1<meta charset="utf-8">, Storage pouch*1<meta charset="utf-8">, Hexkey*1, Type C charging cable, Documents<br></p>`,
