    navCategory: "Desk Setup",
    price: 1899.0,
    comparePrice: 1899.0,
    images: ["https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0348/4948/9034/files/Tail2-4BlueLight.png?v=1751509942", "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0348/4948/9034/files/Tail2-2GreenLight.png?v=1751509942", "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0348/4948/9034/files/Tail2-7.png?v=1751509940"],
    bodyHtml: `<p><img>New Tail, New Tale<br>Revolutionizing live production with OBSBOT Tail 2's innovative PTZR lens design, offering seamless transitions between landscape and portrait modes. Experience unparalleled image quality through our advanced 12-piece optics system, featuring a premium 1/1.5'' CMOS sensor and versatile 12x Hybrid Zoom. Powered by next-generation AI Tracking 2.0, capture subjects with remarkable precision at extended distances. From SDI to NDI, HDMI to UVC, Tail 2 delivers professional-grade connectivity for every production need. New Tail, New Tale - Where Innovation Meets Imagination.<br><br>Where Intelligence Meets Imagination<br>Experience a new realm where years of AI innovation converge to bring your creative vision to life. With enhanced tracking precision, intelligent subject recognition, and boundless customization possibilities, Tail 2 opens the door to a world where your imagination knows no limits.<br><br>Never-lost Tracking with "Only Me"<br>Based on our human tracking algorithm, we develop the new "Only Me" feature ensures unwavering focus on your selected subject, unlike our previous algorithm who will dectect a new target instead, once "Only Me" is activated, tail 2 maintains exclusive tracking of your chosen target, ignoring other potential subjects.<br><br>Professional Framing with Auto Zoom<br>Besides "Only Me", OBSBOT has enhanced its human tracking algorithm with intelligent Auto Zoom technology, which automatically adjusts framing ratios from close-up to half-body and full-body shots. This advanced system maintains optimal subject proportions during tracking movements, delivering professional-quality results without manual adjustments.<br><br>Group Tracking ON, Multiple People Tracked<br>When facing scenarios with multiple person tracking, the group tracking feature in Tail 2 can effectively identify, track, and frame multiple human targets simultaneously, maintaining smooth and stable tracking for everyone in the frame.<br><br>Expanding Trackability: Beyond Human Subjects<br>An expanded range of subjects — including over 30 types of animals and 200 types of objects — can now be instantly recognized and tracked by Tail 2. Based on its object appearance database, OBSBOT's AI algorithm automatically adjusts the frame to keep different shapes of targets centered.<br><br>Start Instant Tracking in Two Clicks<br>Start instant AI tracking for humans, animals, and objects with Double Click Tracking. Simply locate your desired target in the Obsbot Start preview interface and click twice. Our improved recognition engine and expanded database will recognize it immediately with minimal delay.<br><br>Frame the Way You Like Using Composition Lines<br>Adjust the composition lines in real-time to precisely frame your tracking target. Achieve the perfect composition for your creative needs by toggling the crosshair lines on the Obsbot Start app interface.<br><br>Distance-extended Gesture Control<br>Control Tail 2 effortlessly from extended distances with intuitive hand gestures. The device enables AI Tracking activation, Zoom Adjustments, and Recording Control through natural hand movements - making solo content creation seamless and high efficient.<br><br>Next-Generation AI for Professional Virtual Production<br>With AI Tracking integrated into Tail 2, your virtual production process becomes more hands-free, giving you greater freedom to move around without the limitations of traditional fixed camera positions. You can realize more complex actions in your imaginative world with the combination of AI Tracking 2.0 and FreeD protocol support.<br><br>From Distance to Close-up: Seamless Optical Zoom<br>With 5x Optical Zoom in the Tail 2, you can capture clear, detailed footage from greater distances. This powerful feature pushes OBSBOT videography to an ultra level, allowing you to completely immerse yourself in creating rich, professional content with versatile framing options during your video shoots.<br><br>Zoom Closer, See Clearer<br>Thanks to the sleek lens module design and OBSBOT's advanced technology, Tail 2's Hybrid Zoom reaches up to 12x while maintaining excellent image quality and enhancing frame details. This provides you with a more stable and smoother zoom experience during operation.<br><br>Capture Cinematic Tales in Perfect Detail<br>Tail 2 is ready for next-level cinematic live production with its integrated 1/1.5'' CMOS sensor that can capture 50MP resolution video frames. Supporting up to 4K 60fps and 1080P 120fps video capture, every unforgettable detail of your tale will be preserved clearly and stunningly, without any complex preparation needed.<br><br>Steady, Versatile, PTZR Design<br>Featuring the world's first PTZR design 4K camera. Tail 2's exclusively engineered gimbal structure enables 90° lens rotation for seamless vertical 4K image capture. The integrated Auto Leveling System maintains horizontal stability automatically, eliminating the need for manual adjustments.<br><br>Steady, Smooth 3-Axis Stabilization<br>Tail 2 utilizes OBSBOT's new generation stabilization technology to deliver smoother and steadier footage while maintaining image quality, ensuring your dynamic video stays consistently stable.<br><br>Precise, Dynamic, Accurate Focus<br>Powered by All-pixel PDAF (Phase Detection Auto Focus) Technology, Tail 2 delivers lightning-fast and precise autofocus across most lighting conditions. The enhanced focusing system maintains sharp focus on your subject even during dynamic movement, ensuring professional-quality results.<br><br>Two Native ISO Ranges, One Perfect Take<br>With Dual Native ISO tech intergrated, every frame captured by Tail 2 would be well balanced automatically for just excellent video image output, avoiding the overexposure or underexposure situation when capturing videos in various scenarios.<br><br>Clearer Imagine, From Dusk till Dawn<br>Building on OBSBOT Tail Air's acclaimed night shooting capabilities, the Tail 2 creates dazzling clarity in low-light environments. With its enhanced 2μm pixel size sensor and new AI noise reduction algorithm, the Tail 2 delivers stunning, vibrant footage even in challenging dark conditions. Every detail stays sharp and visible, whether you're filming indoors or under the dazzling night sky.<br><br>True-to-life HDR Performance<br>Capture true-to-life colors and details with Tail 2's professional HDR technology. From bright daylight to low-light conditions, every frame stays natural and lifelike, ensuring your content always reflects reality exactly as you see it.<br></p>`,
