    bodyHtml: `<p>The Turtle Beach® Stealth 500 for PS5 &amp; PS4, Windows PCs, Nintendo Switch, &amp; mobile devices redefines what an __ntry-level_ wireless gaming headset is capable of. Easily toggle between 2.4GHz wireless &amp; Bluetooth® connections using the_QuickSwitch button. A staggering battery life of up to 40 hours and an ultra-lightweight, floating headband design with memory foam cushions will keep you locked in the game for hours in complete comfort. Precision-tuned, amplified 40mm drivers along with extensive audio tuning in the Swarm II desktop &amp; mobile apps deliver ultra-clear, customizable audio quality, optimized for spatial audio. Chat with ultra-clear voice accuracy thanks to the omni-directional flip-to-mute microphone._<br><br>Step up to Wireless Freedom<br>Play your favorite games on PS5_ &amp; PS4_, PC, Nintendo Switch_, &amp; mobile devices_with low-latency 2.4GHz wireless and Bluetooth® 5.2 connectivity.<br><br>Best-In-Class Battery Life<br>With up to 40 hours of battery life and quick charge you can enjoy long gaming sessions_without worrying about running out of power.<br><br>QuickSwitch Technology_<br>Easily switch between 2.4GHz wireless &amp; Bluetooth® connections with the built-in_QuickSwitch button. A simple press of the button switches your audio &amp; chat source_between wireless &amp; Bluetooth® devices, enabling you to effortlessly transition between_connections.<br><br>Non-Stop Comfort<br>An ultra-lightweight, floating headband &amp; plush memory foam ear cushions provide a fit_so comfortable, you__l forget you__e even wearing a headset.<br><br>Precise, Amplified Audio<br>40mm drivers are meticulously tuned for precise and powerful spatial audio quality,_giving you a distinct audio advantage over the competition.<br><br>Anywhere Audio Customization<br>Connect to the Swarm_ II desktop software for PC or mobile app for iOS or Android to_access a 10-band audio EQ, audio &amp; microphone presets, and more*. Plus, you can_update the firmware easily using Swarm_ II to ensure your Stealth_ 500 is always up_to date.<br>*Select advanced audio features available in 2.4GHz wireless mode may not be supported in_Bluetooth® mode.<br><br>Ultra-Clear, Flip-to-Mute Mic<br>Chat with precise voice accuracy thanks to the omni-directional flip-to-mute mic that_seamlessly integrates into the headset when not in use.<br><br>Easy Access to Audio Presets<br>Enhance your gameplay experience at the touch of a button with four Turtle Beach_audio presets including Bass Boost, Signature Sound, Treble Boost, and Vocal Boost.<br><br>Advanced Superhuman Hearing®<br>Advanced Superhuman Hearing® brings the same great battlefield advantage of_Superhuman Hearing®, but now with additional adjustability. In the Swarm_ II app,_toggle between three different preset levels and adjust the intensity of Superhuman_Hearing®, to dial-in the perfect sound for a wide range of games.<br><br>Variable Mic Monitoring<br>Avoid shouting thanks to mic monitoring (or sidetone) which allows you to hear your_voice through the headset and adjust monitoring levels on-the-fly with on-ear controls or_in the Swarm_ II app.<br></p>`,
