    bodyHtml: `<p>Matter Certification for Seamless Smart Home Integration<br>With Matter certification, you can enable two SwitchBot Bluetooth devices to support Matter by connecting them to the SwitchBot Relay Switch 1PM. This allows you to control them directly through platforms like Apple Home, Alexa, Google Home, and SmartThings__ll from a single app.</p>
<p>Boost Your Smart Home Network: Built-in Bluetooth Repeater connects up to 10 SwitchBot Bluetooth devices and extends your Bluetooth range up to 262 ft in open spaces, ensuring strong connections across your home.</p>
<p>Transform Your Home Instantly: Make regular lights and appliances smart in just 10 minutes__o rewiring needed! Perfect for wall switches, garden lights, ceiling fans, heaters, and more.</p>
<p>Track Energy Usage Effortlessly: Monitor electricity consumption in real-time, view detailed power reports, and enjoy free 1-year cloud storage to optimize energy use and reduce costs.</p>
<p>Smart, Safe, and Versatile Control: Operate via phone, voice, or schedules, with features like motion-triggered lighting. Built-in protections against overheating and overloads, plus power outage recovery, keep your home secure.<br><br>Material: PC<br>Size: 42x36x16 mm(1.6 x 1.4x0.6 in.)Weight: 27 g (0.9 oz.)Operating Temperature:<br>-20 °C to 40 °C (-5 °F to 105 °F)<br>Operating Humidity:_<br>30% to 70% RH, non-condensing<br>AC Input: 100 to 240 V, 50/60 HzDC Input: 24 to 30 V<br>Max Ac Output Current: 16 AMax DC Output Current: 10 A<br>Connectivity: IEEE 802.11 b/g/n,2.4 GHz Wi-Fi, Bluetooth Low Energy<br></p>`,
