    bodyHtml: `<div data-pf-type="Paragraph" class="sc-djWRfJ dCodXc pf-97_" style="text-align: left;">
<p>Real-Time Notifications (No Hub Needed)<br>After connecting to Wi-Fi, you will be able to receive real-time email and app notifications remotely when dripping, leaking, or flooding is detected, without the need to purchase an additional hub. Share devices with family, and they can also check home status at any time. (2.4Ghz Wi-fi &amp; BLE).<br><br>High Sensitivity Drip Alarms<br>This Device is equipped with four sensor probes at the top and bottom, which can detect a low water level of just 0.5mm. If water pipes drip, and your floor is submerged, or gets wet, it will sound an alarm. Water Leak Detector is compact and convenient in size, suitable for placement in laundry rooms, water heaters, dishwashers, sinks, and other places.<br><br>Water Level Detection<br>Equipped with a 1-meter extended probe, you'll be able to detect changes in water levels of places like swimming pools, bathtubs, and fish tanks. It can also be placed in narrower areas, such as inside refrigerators or washing machines. And is suitable for homes, warehouses, basements, sinks, water heaters, pipelines, and more.<br><br>Includes Loud Alarm Sounds<br>To help you stay alert, We've included 100dB high pitched alarms, which means even if there is a leak in basements or places a little further away, you'll know in a timely manner. Once Discovered, you can manually set it back to mute without worrying about noise issues.<br><br>IP67 Waterproof &amp; Up to 2 Years Battery Life<br>Water Leak Detector is designed with a fully sealed waterproof shell and can easily handle high humidity working environments. It comes with 2 x AAA batteries and has a battery lifespan of up to 2 Years. When Battery is low, our app will also send notifications to remind you to replace them in a timely manner. (*When used in Standy-by Mode, actual battery life performance may vary depending on use).<br><br>Part of SwitchBot Ecosystem, Voice Command Compatible<br>Use With SwitchBot Plug Mini or Indoor Cam, and remotely turn off electrical equipment or check the condition of your house in case of leakage. It can also support third-party services such as Alexa/Google/Siri/IFTTT/SmartThings.<br></p>
<p>Color: White<br>Material: ABS<br>Size:78 x32 x 32 mm (3.1 x 1.3 x1.3 in.)<br>Weight: 70 g (2.5 oz.)<br>Noise Level:100 dB_<br>Water Resistance: IP67<br>Power: 2 AAA batteries_<br>Battery Life: Approx. 2 years<br>Operating Temperature: 0 'C to 40 °C (32 °F to 104 °F)<br>Operating Humidity: 0 to 99 % RH<br>Connectivity: 2.4 GHz Wi-Fi; Bluetooth Low Energy 4.2 or above<br>System Requirements: iOS 14.0+, Android OS 5.0+<br></p>
</div>`,
