    bodyHtml: `<p>Pure and simple.<br data-mce-fragment="1">On the road to high-tech, feature-packed earbuds, some brands have forgotten what people really want — comfortable, stylish earbuds with full, clear sound. We haven’t forgotten. Smokin’ Buds look great and they sound better. Sure, they come with intuitive touch controls, sweat- and water-resistant construction and a mic in each earbud. But the priority is big, clean sound and lots of it.<br data-mce-fragment="1"><br>Built around sound.<br data-mce-fragment="1">Smokin’ Buds feature drivers that have been selected and expertly tuned, plus EQ modes that deliver the best audio quality for music, movies or podcasts. They also incorporate our most comfortable, ergonomic design ever — developed through extensive research and testing for a perfect, noise-isolating fit.<br data-mce-fragment="1"><br data-mce-fragment="1">Passion in action.<br data-mce-fragment="1">Skullcandy was born in the mountains. We’re passionate about the environment and we’re working hard to make every new product more environmentally friendly. Smokin’ Buds feature 50% certified recycled plastics and, like every Skullcandy product, 100% recyclable packaging.<br data-mce-fragment="1"><br data-mce-fragment="1">20 Hours Battery Life + Rapid Charge<br data-mce-fragment="1">IPX4 Sweat &amp; Water Resistant<br data-mce-fragment="1">Skullcandy Supreme Sound™<br>Made of 50% Certified Recycled Plastics<br data-mce-fragment="1">Music, Movie &amp; Podcast EQ Modes<br data-mce-fragment="1"><br data-mce-fragment="1">Call &amp; Media Controls<br data-mce-fragment="1">Additional Features &amp; Info<br data-mce-fragment="1">8 Hours in the Bud + 12 Hours in the Case<br data-mce-fragment="1">Rapid Charge (10 mins = 2 Hours of playtime)<br data-mce-fragment="1">Premium Audio Quality<br data-mce-fragment="1">Activate Voice Assistant<br data-mce-fragment="1">Capacitive Touch Controls<br data-mce-fragment="1">Microphone in Each Earbud<br data-mce-fragment="1">Noise-Isolating Fit<br data-mce-fragment="1">Use Either Bud Solo<br data-mce-fragment="1"><br>Headphone Type: True Wireless In-Ear<br data-mce-fragment="1">Connection Type: Bluetooth® 5.1<br data-mce-fragment="1">Impedance: 16Ω±15%<br data-mce-fragment="1">Driver Diameter: 6mm<br data-mce-fragment="1">THD: &lt;3%<br data-mce-fragment="1">Sound Pressure Level: 104dB±3dB<br data-mce-fragment="1">Frequency Response: 20Hz – 20KHz<br data-mce-fragment="1">Weight: 40.59g<br data-mce-fragment="1"><br data-mce-fragment="1">What’s in the box:<br data-mce-fragment="1">Smokin’ Buds True Wireless Earbuds<br data-mce-fragment="1">Charging Case<br data-mce-fragment="1">Ear Gels (S, M, L)<br data-mce-fragment="1">USB-C Charging Cable<br data-mce-fragment="1">Quick Start Guide<br data-mce-fragment="1">User Guide<br data-mce-fragment="1"></p>`,
