    bodyHtml: `<p>Rediscover simplicity with Jib USB-C. This no-frills, plug-and-play earbud connects instantly to your phone or laptop—no charging, no pairing, no fuss. Just crisp audio, total control of your calls and media with the in-line mic/remote, and a direct connection for those who value ease over extras.<br><br>PLUG IN, PLAY ON - USB-C Connection:<br>Get back to basics with a direct connection to your device. Nothing standing between you and your music. No extra steps with Bluetooth pairing. Never worrying about a dead battery. Just an instant connection, every time.<br><br>CONTROLS AT YOUR FINGERTIPS - In-line microphone/remote​: Take calls. Answer or end your phone call. Play and pause your music. Skip forward to the next track. You’re in control with the easy-to-use in-line microphone/remote.<br><br>PURE SOUND, PERFECT FIT - Noise isolating fit​: Jib USB-C provides a comfortable, noise isolating fit for all day listening. Including 3 different-sized ear gels to help you find the perfect fit and block out external noises.<br></p>`,
