    images: ["https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0348/4948/9034/files/CrusherEvo_AllLove_S6EVW-R790_Hero-2_v001.png?v=1736760048", "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0348/4948/9034/files/CrusherEvo_AllLove_S6EVW-R790_Back_v001.png?v=1736760048", "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0348/4948/9034/files/CrusherEvo_AllLove_S6EVW-R790_Front_v001.png?v=1736760048"],
    bodyHtml: `<p><strong>CRUSHER® BASS: ANYTHING ELSE IS JUST AN IMITATION.</strong><br>Skullcandy Crusher is the original, one-and-only immersive sensory bass experience. Use the Crusher Bass slider to perfectly adjust the bass level: Turn it down for mellow bass. Turn it up to really rattle your bones. What’s more, Crusher Evo features audio quality improvements over original Crusher so you’ll hear an even broader range of bass and deeper, richer sound.</p>
<p><strong>LONGER LISTENING WITH 40 HOURS OF BATTERY LIFE.</strong><br>You don’t have time to plug in your headphones every time you turn around. That’s why we’ve engineered Crusher Evo with a full 40 hours of battery. Plus, whenever you start to get low, the Rapid Charge feature gives you an extra 4 hours of listening time from just a quick 10-minute charge.</p>
<p><strong>TUNE FOR YOUR HEARING WITH PERSONAL SOUND IN THE SKULLCANDY APP.</strong><br>No one’s hearing is the same. That’s why we want to help you optimize your audio for your unique hearing. Audiodo™ technology in the Skullcandy App analyzes the hearing in your left and right ear, then creates a Personal Sound Profile that is used to adjust the audio to optimal levels for your specific hearing. That profile is then stored on your headphones so you’ll experience sounds in your audio that you’ve never experienced before.</p>
<p><strong>DON’T WORRY. YOU’VE GOT TILE™.</strong><br>Crusher Evo features the built-in capabilities of Tile finding technology. If you ever misplace your headphones, you can easily “ring” them from the Skullcandy App. So what might have seemed lost, is now quickly found.</p>
<p><strong>FEATURES<br></strong>Adjustable Sensory Bass<br>Personal Sound by Audiodo™<br>Wireless via Bluetooth® 5<br>Up to 40 Hours of Battery<br>Rapid Charge: 10 Minutes = 4 Hours<br>Call, Track and Volume Control<br>Activate Assistant<br>Built-in Tile™ Finding Technology<br>Flat-folding and Collapsible<br>Compatible with Skullcandy App<br>Travel Bag<br>Back-Up AUX Cable<br>USB-C Charging Cable<br><br></p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0348/4948/9034/files/a-plus-content-1_480x480.jpg?v=1599460502" alt=""><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0348/4948/9034/files/a-plus-content-2_480x480.jpg?v=1599460507" alt=""><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0348/4948/9034/files/a-plus-content-3_480x480.jpg?v=1599460510" alt=""><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0348/4948/9034/files/a-plus-content-4_480x480.jpg?v=1599460514" alt=""></p>`,
