    bodyHtml: `<p><span>Meet Skull-iQ Smart Feature Technology. Hands-free Voice Control gives you absolute authority over your audio using only your voice — and that’s just the beginning.</span></p>
<h3 translate="no" class="productStorytelling-heading notranslate">Earbuds that listen to YOU.</h3>
<p class="large">Voice Control means you never need to take off your gloves or let go of the handlebar. Play, pause, adjust volume, take calls, skip tracks, launch Spotify and activate Stay-Aware Mode, all without ever touching your device.</p>
<h3 translate="no" class="productStorytelling-heading notranslate">Buds so smart they learn.</h3>
<p class="large">The days of buying new earbuds to get the latest features are over. Skull-iQ gives us the ability to push new features and updates to your earbuds via the Skullcandy App as they become available.</p>
<h3 translate="no" class="productStorytelling-heading notranslate">Worry-free wireless.</h3>
<p class="large">With comfortable ear hangers and an IP55 sweat and water-resistant rating, Push Active is built for tough workouts and intense adventures. We also included Tile® finding technology — just in case.</p>
<h3 translate="no" class="productStorytelling-heading notranslate">Hours of power.</h3>
<p class="large">Push Active delivers a whopping 44 hours of listening time between the charging case and buds. Plus, your earbuds tell you how much battery is left every time you remove them from the case.</p>`,
