    bodyHtml: `<p>Introducing Arc II Music, the next generation of our open-ear earbuds series. We've enhanced the open-earbud experience, which we were among the first to introduce, with several improvements. <br><br>Arc II Music offers more flexible ear hooks for improved comfort, a 6-axis head motion sensor for hands-free control, IPX5 water and sweat resistance, and longer battery life with an upgraded charging case. With Bluetooth 5.3 and Multipoint Connectivity, you can pair and seamlessly switch between multiple audio sources, such as a tablet and your phone.<br><br>Open-Ear Design with Flexible Ear Hook<br>Arc II Music is designed to sit comfortably in your ears without blocking surrounding noise. They come with a special ear hook and hinge design that offers better shape and flexibility for a snug and comfortable fit.<br><br>Sweat-proof<br>Arc II Music boasts enhanced durability with an IPX5 water resistance rating, ensuring it can endure any workout intensity.<br><br>Hands-Free Control<br>Apart from easy touch controls, Arc II Music also includes a high-tech 6-axis motion sensor. With this, you can simply move your head to answer or finish calls and manage music without using your hands.<br><br>Powerful Sound<br>Experience your favorite music tracks with vibrant and powerful sound that doesn't compromise on volume and bass. 16.2mm drivers paired with Snapdragon Sound directs clear and vibrant audio straight to your ears.<br><br>All-Day Battery Life<br>Arc II boasts a sleek new design. The updated slim case now offers an additional 27 hours of battery life. This means you can enjoy your music on the move without needing to plug in.<br><br>Cleer+ App<br>With the Cleer+ App, you have the power to tailor your EQ settings and music playback just the way you like. You can also customize device controls and get firmware updates. Find it on both the Apple App Store and Google Play.<br></p>`,
