    bodyHtml: `<p>5MP Ultra High-Def, For a Clearer Kind of Protection<br>Pan/Tilt Cam Plus 3K features a 5MP pixel lens paired with a high-res lens module that can capture clearer images and more realistic colors, making every move visible. Its perfect for watching over pets, loved ones or even insects and plants. Supports 2.4GHz Wi-Fi and can be set up in just a few minutes.<br><br>Clearer Images, Both Day &amp; Night<br>You can now see colorful images even in low light environments for longer duration. Equipped with 8 infrared LEDs, night vision distance can reach up to 10 meters with images staying clear. 940nm invisible infrared light also means no disturbances when sleeping, making it perfect for even baby rooms.<br><br>4-way Split-Screen Viewing, with No Dead Angles<br>This camera provides a wide horizontal 360 degree and vertical 115 degree field of view, and can be controlled via our app to look wherever you want. It also supports 6 placement points to help quickly view areas that matter most. Use Split-Screen viewing to check multiple places simultaneously without switching.<br><br>AI Detection with Intuitive Alarms<br>Our indoor safety camera is equipped with AI human recognition technology, to accurately detect movement with three sensitivity level adjustments to prevent recognition error. Once motion is captured, your camera will immediately start tracking and recording activity of any objects in view, and push real-time alerts to you, ensuring that you don't miss anything important.<br><br>Voice Contol &amp; Two-Way Talk<br>You can control this device with simple voice commands to do things like activate security mode when leaving home. Which means if someone enters your house, Echo Show will automatically sound an alarm and alert you. And when coming home, simply say "Alexa, turn on Privacy Mode" and Pan/Tilt Cam will hide its lens to protect your privacy. Supports Two-Way Talk to enable you to communicate with whoever is by your camera when you're not at home.<br><br>Flexible Storage Options<br>There are two different ways to store footage, locally or via the cloud. Local storage supports up to 256GB SD cards, and continuous recording can last up to 512 hours. Cloud storage adopts AES-128 Encryption Technology to ensure security and also comes with a 14-day free trial. Turn on continuous or event recording to record the activities of pets and children at home and replay them at any time, every moment is a memory.<br><br>Power Input: 5 V 2 A (USB-C)<br>Video Resolution: 3K<br>Field of View: 107° diagonal<br>Pan/Tilt Angle: 360° horizontal, 115° vertical<br>Storage: Supports FAT32 formatted microSD card<br>up to 256 GB (Not included)<br>Operating Temperature:__15 _ to 45 __(5 ºF to 113 ºF )<br>Operating Humidity:__95 % RH<br>Network Connectivity: 802.11b/g/n, 2.4 GHz<br></p>`,
