    bodyHtml: `<p class="irIKAp">Upgraded Stabilization iSteady 7.0 Algorithm​.<br>The newest iSteady 7.0 stabilization system ​takes your smartphone shooting to the next level, ​ allowing you to create smooth on-the-move footage ​with ease. It is improved by 30% as anti-shake as the previous generation and has more powerful motors that operate more efficiently.​<br><br>Lighter Weight​ Better Hold​<br>Weight 259g​<br><br>This is the most lightweight<br>3-axis smartphone gimbal for creators on the move.​<br><br>As Compact as an iPhone​<br>Tiny enough to fit in the pocket, so you can easily take it along for any adventure.​<br><br>Carry Large Smartphone with High-Torque Motor ​<br>The motor torques have been improved by 30%, ensuring that your phone can stay where it needs to be, even when carrying larger smartphones. ​<br><br>Compatible with Almost All Sizes of Smartphone​ (iPhone, HUAWEI, Xiaomi, OPPO, VIVO, etc.)<br><br>Independently Magnetic Fill Light​<br>Magnetic Installation​<br>Cold/Warm/Natural White Light​<br>10-Level Adjustable Brightness​<br>Still works without being magnetized to iSteady XE<br><br>Simplified Control ​<br>Quickly enable Inception Mode (spin shot) by simply pressing the function button three times.​<br>Quickly switch between Landscape and Portrait Mode by pressing function button once. ​<br>Quickly switch between gimbal modes (PF/PTF/L/POV) by simply pressing M button once​<br><br><br>Tech Specification<br>Weight​ : 259g (excluding fill light &amp; tripod)​<br>Main Material​ : High-Performance Composites​<br>Max Payload : (280g​)<br>Phone Width : (55mm~90mm​)<br>Battery Capacity​ : (3.7V / 2000mAh​)<br>Charging time​ : (2.5hrs)​<br>Battery Life : (8hrs)​<br>Mechanical Range​ : (Pan: 320°) (Roll: 320°) (Tilt: 320°)​<br>Working Temperature​ : (-10 - +45℃​)</p>
<p class="irIKAp">Motor Protection​<br>The motor can be protected from damage caused by improper operation by having the gimbal powered off automatically.​</p>
<p class="irIKAp">Standard Accessory​<br>Tripod, Carrying Case, USB-C Charging Cable​<br><br>Fill Light Specifications​ : (For XE KIT Only)<br>(Weight: 16g​)<br>Battery Capacity : 3.7V/300mAh​<br>Power: 1W​<br>Battery Life: 1 hour​<br>Lights: Cold Light (6500k), Warm Light (3000k), Natural White Light (5500k)​<br><br>M Button<br>Press and hold for 3s : Power on/off gimbal​<br>Press once: ​ Switch between working modes (PTF-PF-L-POV)<br>Press twice: ​ Standby mode (Press any button to exit)​<br><br>Working Mode Indicator​<br>Battery Level Indicator​<br><br>Display gimbal mode : If one of working modes is in use, its mode light will be in solid green.​<br>Display battery level:​ Long pressing Function button to check out battery level.​</p>`,
