    bodyHtml: `<p><span style="color: black;">The iSteady M6 is a professional 3-axis smartphone stabilizer ideal for vloggers, live-streamers, vacationers and filmmakers who want to create smooth and steady content.</span></p><p> </p><p> <span style="color: black;">It features a magnetic fill light integrated with an AI vision sensor, which offers face and object tracking during the day or at night.</span></p><p> </p><p> <span style="color: black;">Its upgraded 3-axis structure offers free movement from all angles. Plus, its 360° infinite panning rotation, iSteady 7.0 anti-shake system and much more empower you to get stunning and epic shots even while solo filmmaking.</span></p><p> </p><p> <span style="color: black;">Features</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">Magnetic Fill Light Integrated with AI Vision Sensor</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">iSteady 7.0 Anti-Shake Algorithm</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">Free Angle Movement</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">0.91“OLED Display</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">360° Infinite Spin Shot</span></p><p> </p><p> <span style="color: black;">HELLO, NEW EXPERIENCE TO ENJOY</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">Magnetic Fill Light</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">Integrated with AI Vision Sensor</span></p><p> </p><p> <span style="color: black;">Rear Camera Tracking Feasible</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">Magnetically Removable AI Vision Sensor</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">With removable AI-powered sensor, you can switch between the front and rear camera to achieve flexible "Follow You" with ease no matter if you are facing or facing away from the phone screen.</span></p><p> </p><p> <span style="color: black;">AI Tracking In All Mobile Apps</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">Full Camera Control for Social Media Video Creation</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">Thanks to its built-in AI vision sensor, the AI tracking can be enabled in all mobile apps including the native camera app and beauty apps, even if the gimbal-exclusive app is not connected to gimbal device.</span></p><p> </p><p> <span style="color: black;">Magnetic Fill Light with Different Brightness</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">Light up Your Creativity</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">Different lighting for your diverse style of filming: Cold light, warm light and RGB light at your choices to bring out details in and add dynamism to your shots.</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">Color temperature: 2700K - 6500K</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">Create fantastic effects without gel filters.</span></p><p> </p><p> <span style="color: black;">UPGRADED 3-AXIS DESIGN</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">UNLOCK CREATIVE POSIBILITY</span></p><p> </p><p> <span style="color: black;">Dual Sided Powering On</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">Ultra-Wide-Angle Shots Made Easy</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">The gimbal can be powered on whether your phone is in front of or behind the roll motor.</span></p><p> </p><p> <span style="color: black;">335° tilt rotation</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">The professional gimbal with 335° tilt rotation and wider space between axes offers smooth movements from all perspectives, even in extreme low angle, allowing you to make blockbusters with ease.</span></p><p> </p><p> <span style="color: black;">iSteady 7.0 Stabilization</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">Capture That Moment with Precision and Clarity</span></p><p> </p><p> <span style="color: black;">iSteady M6 integrates the advanced iSteady 7.0 stabilization algorithms, helping users to capture on-the-move and shake-free creations that wow. To put it another way, no matter if you are walking or running, you can always film with flawless stabilization and create ultra-smooth footage.</span></p><p> </p><p> <span style="color: black;">360° INFINITE SPIN SHOT</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">Expand Your Creativity</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">Inception shooting without app. Just press the M button three times in a row to enable the Inception mode and you will see 360° infinite panning which rotates your phone's camera 360° indefinitely. No gorgeous moment gets left out.</span></p><p> </p><p> <span style="color: black;">*In addition to Inception Mode, there're versatile working modes including PF, PTF, POV, L and S (Sport Mode) to add more pizzas to your shots.</span></p><p> </p><p> <span style="color: black;">0.91” OLED DISPLAY</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">Working Status at a Glance</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">The OLED display visualizes almost all gimbal status and you can conveniently check various gimbal parameters, Bluetooth status, battery level, gimbal mode and so on.</span></p><p> </p><p> <span style="color: black;">POWERFUL MOTOR WITH HIGH TORQUES</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">Up To 400g Payload</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">3 powerful motors supporting payload up to 400g, make sure your smartphone stays where it needs to be.</span></p><p> </p><p> <span style="color: black;">The four 1/4"-20 UNC ports allow multiple accessories to be added to unlock creative potential of your iSteady M6.</span></p><p> </p><p> <span style="color: black;">REVERSE-CHARGE TECHNOLOGY</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">Charging Your Phone</span></p><p> <span style="color: black;">18h Battery Life | 2600mAh</span></p><p> </p><p> <span style="color: black;">It supports reverse charging and the battery can last up to 18 hours of continuous usage. You can charge your smartphone via the power-out port on the gimbal while you are recording video, without suffering from low-battery anxiety any more.</span></p>`,
