    bodyHtml: `Welcome to Skullcandy SLYR Pro: the expert gaming headset for seasoned gamers looking to sharpen up their skills with cutting-edge, play-enhancing audio quality and features. SLYR Pro delivers all-day comfort and reliable performance — so players can give their gameplay a buff, without the steep price tag.<br><br>SKULLCANDY SUPREME SOUND, TUNED TO YOU<br data-mce-fragment="1">Dynamic and expertly tuned drivers with the ability to personalize to your unique hearing, so you’ll pick up every audio detail — down to the most distant footstep. Plus, a range of intuitive features for advanced and uninterrupted gameplay.<br data-mce-fragment="1">• 50mm drivers for premium audio quality.<br data-mce-fragment="1">• Enhanced Sound Perception (ESP): create a unique Personal Sound profile via the Skull-HQ PC app for a more personalized audio experience.<br data-mce-fragment="1">• Advanced and custom EQ modes (gaming, movies, music, podcasts) available through the Skull-HQ PC App.<br data-mce-fragment="1">• Easy-access, on-headset volume and mute controls.<br><br>CRYSTAL CLEAR COMMUNICATION<br data-mce-fragment="1">Multiplayer games require perfectly coordinated teamwork, and communication is key. SLYR Pro’s Clear Voice Smart Mic isolates the speaker’s voice and cuts out background noise — and secondary mics in the headset mean you can communicate clearly, even with the boom removed.<br data-mce-fragment="1">• Clear Voice Smart Mic: artificial intelligence-driven technology removes unwanted background noise for crystal-clear audio transmission.<br data-mce-fragment="1">- Feature compatible with both detachable boom mic + built-in mic.<br data-mce-fragment="1">• Mic-status LED indicating whether the user is on mute (or not).<br><br>PLAY-ALL-DAY PERFORMANCE DESIGN<br data-mce-fragment="1">Bring on the marathon, all-day gaming sessions — SLYR Pro is so comfortable you’ll forget you’re even wearing a headset.<br data-mce-fragment="1">• Lightweight design with tough, flexible materials that stand up to hours (and hours) of play.<br data-mce-fragment="1">• Comfortable memory foam ear cups with a noise-isolating fit.<br data-mce-fragment="1">• Moisture-wicking and breathable spandex ear cup material.<br data-mce-fragment="1">• 20 hours total battery with Rapid Charge for all-day gaming marathons.<br data-mce-fragment="1">- While wired, ESP &amp; Clear Voice Smart Mic require the onboard battery to function.<br data-mce-fragment="1">• Rapid Charge (20 minutes = 2 hours).<br data-mce-fragment="1">• Will charge if connected to select devices via USB-A to USB-C cables.<br><br>SKULL-HQ SOFTWARE<br data-mce-fragment="1">Seamless compatibility with the free PC software for personalized features and control. Skull-HQ software features include:<br data-mce-fragment="1">• ESP Test: tunes headset to user’s unique hearing with custom listening profile.<br data-mce-fragment="1">• Sidetone: allows users to adjust how they hear themselves through headset.<br data-mce-fragment="1">• Gaming / chat mix: allows users to balance audio and chat levels according to personal preference.<br data-mce-fragment="1">• Amount of vocal pickup from microphones.<br data-mce-fragment="1">• Preset and custom EQ settings.<br data-mce-fragment="1">• General device information: battery life, update notifications, support, etc.<br><br>MULTIPLATFORM CONNECTIVITY<br data-mce-fragment="1">Welcome to the versatile advantage. SLYR Pro provides crystal clear audio on PC, Playstation, Switch, Xbox, mobile and more so you can level-up your listening on any platform.<br data-mce-fragment="1">• Wired compatibility with any gaming device that accepts USB-A or 3.5mm aux audio connectivity.<br data-mce-fragment="1">• Includes USB-C to USB-A (4ft) and 3.5mm aux cable (4ft).<br>`,
