    bodyHtml: `<p>Go hands-free with our vegan-leather shoulder strap. In 3 color mixes and compatible with all Polaroid speakers and instant cameras.<br><br>Wear it your way.<br data-mce-fragment="1">Shoulder, wrist, neck, head: we don’t judge. All you need to know is that it’s comfy thanks to its soft, stretchy fabric.<br><br>Universally loved.<br data-mce-fragment="1">This shoulder strap can be used on all Polaroid instant cameras and music players.<br><br>Tech Specs<br>- Vegan-leather<br data-mce-fragment="1">- Shoulder strap length<br data-mce-fragment="1">- 3 colors available<br data-mce-fragment="1">- Compatible with Polaroid speakers &amp; instant cameras<br></p>`,
