    bodyHtml: `<p>Motion Sensor Detects Your Movements<br>With a motion detection range of up to almost 30 feet within 110° horizontally and 55° vertically, there__ more than enough range to secure an entire room of your home. You__e also able to customize the sensitivity settings so that you are only alerted to movements that matter to you. With the built-in light sensor, it will automatically trigger the SwitchBot Bot to turn on the light if someone moves when the environment gets dark.<br><br>Easy to Install &amp; Long Battery Life<br>Thanks to its small and wireless design, SwitchBot Motion Sensor can be installed and set up in seconds. You can place it anywhere since its magnetic flexible base can be inserted to the bottom and side. The included battery provides up to 3 years of power for round-the-clock security.<br><br>Part of SwitchBot Ecosystem &amp; Compatible with Alexa<br>Connect Motion Sensor with other SwitchBot products and set up a __cene_ in the SwitchBot app. When you come home, SwitchBot Bot (button pusher) will automatically be triggered to turn on the light, and Alexa will say __elcome home_. When you leave, SwitchBot Indoor Camera will automatically turn on to detect indoor activity while you__e away (SwitchBot Hub required).<br><br>Remote Alert Notification<br>You will receive a notification if a suspicious person enters the house while you are away. (SwitchBot Hub required)<br><br>Energy &amp; Money Saving<br>By detecting the room vacant, Motion Sensor automatically turns off the lights, reducing unnecessary energy consumption to save you money.<br><br>Size: Motion Sensor: 54 _ 54 _ 30 mm_(2.1 _ 2.1 _ 1.2 in.);<br>Base: 45 _ 45 _ 32 mm (1.8 _ 1.8 _ 1.3 in.)<br>Weight: Motion Sensor: 56 g (2 oz.) (with_batteries);<br>Base: 19 g (0.7 oz.)<br>Battery Life: 2 AAA batteries, roughly 3 years_(triggered 120 times by motion, 40 times by_light sensing and 20 times by local scenes_daily under 25 _ [77 __)<br>Operating Temperature: _10 _ to 60 __(14 _ to 140 _)<br>Operating Humidity: 20 % to 85 % RH<br>Maximum Detection Distance: 9 m (29.5 ft.)<br>Maximum Detection Range: 110° horizontal_and 55° vertical (results obtained from lab_experiments under 25 _ [77 __)</p>`,
