    images: ["https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0348/4948/9034/products/14_b7ae1408-314b-46a5-bc23-7fdc85e28707.png?v=1663737402", "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0348/4948/9034/products/prod_45b3758a-d283-4347-8673-e9ba1822e766.jpg?v=1738901388", "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0348/4948/9034/products/prod_9e5b3b06-93ac-4f11-b3d2-a0ffd6539804.jpg?v=1738901388"],
    bodyHtml: `<p>Smart Feature Technology</p>
<p>Welcome to next-level listening</p>
<p>Introducing Grind with Skull-iQ Smart Feature Technology. Hands-free Voice Control gives you absolute authority over your audio using only your voice — and that’s just the beginning.</p>
<p>Earbuds that listen to YOU.</p>
<p>Voice Control means you never need to drop what you’re doing. Play, pause, adjust volume, skip tracks, answer calls, launch Spotify®, activate Stay-Aware Mode and more, all without ever touching your device.</p>
<p>A full suite of sweet features.</p>
<p>Skull-iQ is more than just Voice Control. Share audio with a friend in real time, activate your assistant and receive over-the-air updates through the Skullcandy App as they become available.</p>
<p>Buds so smart they learn.</p>
<p>The days of buying new earbuds to get the latest features are over. Skull-iQ gives us the ability to push new features and updates to your earbuds via the Skullcandy App as they become available.</p>
<p>Hours of power.</p>
<p>Grind delivers a whopping 40 hours of listening time between the charging case and buds. Plus, your earbuds tell you how much battery is left every time you remove them from the case.</p>
<p>Track ‘em down with Tile.</p>
<p>Built-in Tile finding technology makes it easy to track down lost earbuds. Misplaced your buds? Just ‘ring’ them from the Tile app.</p>`,
