    bodyHtml: `Most sound-limiting headphones aren’t exactly engineered to deliver a great sound experience. Not true for Cassette™️ Junior. We apply the same premium sound engineering, testing and quality standards to Cassette™️ Junior as all Skullcandy headphones. Then we simply limit the volume to prevent over-exposure to higher sound levels.<br><br>BUILT-IN MICROPHONE.<br>Cassette™️ Junior features an easy microphone for interacting with online games and video calls<br><br>FOLD AND GO.<br>With a rugged, innovative hinge design, Cassette™️ Junior quickly and easily collapses down to go anywhere you go.<br><br>MULTI-HOUR COMFORT.<br>With soft ear cushions and a lightweight headband, Cassette™️ Junior is designed for comfort. Perfect for those long flights or car rides.<br><br>Volume Limited to 85 db<br>Premium Sound<br>Comfortable Ear Cushions<br>Microphone<br>Collapsible Design<br>3.5mm Audio Jack<br>`,
