    bodyHtml: `<p>The compact protective case fits perfectly to the e-mark’s shape and protects it optimally against external impacts.<br><br>PRODUCT FEATURES<br>- Compact and perfect fit to the e-mark<br>- Lightweight and robust material<br>- Ideal protection against scratches, splash water, smaller shakes and other external impacts<br></p>`,
