    bodyHtml: `<meta charset="utf-8">
<p><span>The Steelie Dash Mount Kit Plus offers twice the holding power of our Dash Mount Kit, making it perfect for plus-sized devices. This patented magnetic two piece ball-and-socket mounting kit allows you to effortlessly attach your phone to your dashboard. The Plus Kit also includes the MultiStick Adapter for ultimate versatility, allowing you to easily remove and restick the magnetic socket multiple times.</span></p>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<h3>PRODUCT INFORMATION</h3>
<p>The beauty of the Steelie Dash Mount Kit Plus is in its simplicity. This magnetic two piece ball-and-socket mounting system attaches to your dashboard using a strong, removable 3M® VHB® adhesive. The Magnetic Phone Socket Plus features a powerful neodymium magnet and offers twice the holding power as our standard-sized magnetic socket making it perfect for both standard and plus-sized devices with or without a case. With two convenient ways to attach your magnet to your device, you can decide whether to keep the phone-safe magnet on your phone all the time or use the MultiStick™ Adapter which allows you to remove and restick the Magnetic Phone Socket Plus multiple times. The Steelie Magnetic Phone Socket Plus contains a silicone center, creating a smooth glide and firm grip that allows you to easily adjust the phone for the perfect viewing angle.</p>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<p>A great bonus feature to this product is its versatility. With the Steelie Magnetic Phone Socket Plus you can easily attach your phone to other magnetic surfaces like refrigerator doors, toolboxes, and our entire ecosystem of Steelie Magnetic Mounts.<br><br>Why use the multistick adapter?</p>
<p>For the times when you want to be magnet-free -<br></p>
<ul>
<li>Easily move your magnetic socket between devices + cases</li>
<li>MultiStick adhesive holds strong, removes quickly, and resticks multiple times</li>
<li>Hardshell case required for glass-backed phones</li>
</ul>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<h3>PRODUCT DETAILS</h3>
<ul>
<li>Dash Mount attaches anywhere on dash using 3M® VHB® adhesive</li>
<li>Magnetic Phone Socket Plus features a powerful neodymium magnet and silicone center to provide a strong grip and smooth glide</li>
<li>The Plus Kit includes the Magnetic Phone Socket Plus that offers twice the holding power of our standard Magnetic Phone Socket, making it perfect for plus-sized devices while being safe to use with all phones and tablets</li>
<li>Two ways to attach your Magnetic Phone Socket Plus! Attach directly to devices using 3M® VHB® foam adhesive or onto the included MultiStick Adapter to easily remove and restick your magnet multiple times</li>
<li>Steelie Dash Mount features high-quality steel ball press fit into a machined aluminium base for elegant look and durable functionality</li>
<li>3M® VHB® foam adhesive can be removed without damage to surfaces</li>
<li>Adjusts and holds in any viewing angle</li>
<li>Magnetic Phone Socket Plus works with all other mounts in the Steelie ecosystem, allowing you to use the world's finest magnetic mounting system whether you're in your vehicle, office, garage, home, or on the go</li>
<li>NOTE: MultiStick Adapter requires hardshell case for glass-backed phones</li>
<li>Includes Dash Mount, Magnetic Phone Socket Plus, one replacement 3M® VHB® adhesive pad for Dash Mount, one replacement 3M® VHB® adhesive pad for Magnetic Phone Socket Plus, MultiStick Adapter, and installation kit</li>
</ul>`,
