    bodyHtml: `<p> </p>
<h2><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>PRODUCT INFORMATION</strong></span></h2>
<p>Steelie products are designed to interchange with one another. Our large selection of mounts and magnetic sockets allow you to expand your Steelie Ecosystem to the home, office, or on the go while giving you full control over whether you want your magnetic socket to live on your phone or on the mount.<span> </span></p>
<p> </p>
<p><span>New device? No need to purchase a new Steelie Pedestal Kit. Simply remove the existing adhesive, replace it with a brand new one, and you are ready to go. Each kit contains: 2 x 3M® VHB™ Adhesive Pads, and 2 x cleaning pads.</span></p>
<p><span><br></span></p>`,
